comments.raw_text:
>+#urlbar[pageproxystate="invalid"][focused="true"] > #urlbar-stop-button,

>+#urlbar-reload-button[displaystop] + #urlbar-stop-button + #urlbar-go-button {
>   visibility: collapse;
> }

With this we display no button at all when loading a page and focusing the url bar.

